《时空幻境》于Xbox Live Arcade上发售后，立刻就大获好评，如评论网站[[MetaCritic|MetaCritic]]累计评析分数达到93%。<ref name="metacritic"/>这使得该游戏荣登Xbox Live最佳游戏的宝座<ref>{{cite web | url = http://braid-game.com/news/?p=303 | title = Braid is the highest-rated XBLA game ever. (Also, sales data). | first = Jonathan | last = Blow | publisher = Braid-game.com | date = 2008-08-09 | accessdate = 2009-02-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081219220930/http://braid-game.com/news/?p=303 | archive-date = 2008-12-19 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，并且截至2009年2月20日为止身居Xbox 360评价最高游戏第10名。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metacritic.com/games/xbox360/ | title = Xbox 360 Game Reviews from MetaCritic | publisher = [[MetaCritic|MetaCritic]] | accessdate = 2009-02-20 | archive-date = 2009-02-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090218183606/http://www.metacritic.com/games/xbox360/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>《时空幻境》发售后第一周内内超过55,000人购买本游戏。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://braid-game.com/news/?p=323 | title = Stats: The First Week of Braid | first = Jonathan | last = Blow | date = 2008-08-13 | accessdate = 2009-02-20 | publisher = Braid-game.com | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150130024043/http://braid-game.com/news/?p=323 | archive-date = 2015-01-30 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>据布洛说，本作是2008年销量第二大的 Xbox Live Arcade游戏。<ref name="nowgamer">{{cite web | url = http://www.nowgamer.com/news/307/braid-has-been-very-profitable-for-creator | title = Braid has been "very profitable" for creator | publisher = Now Gamer | date =2009-03-18 | accessdate = 2009-04-11 | first = Christopher | last = Reynolds }}</ref>布洛表示该游戏销售「非常赚钱」，获得的收入比他若在开发游戏期间转去做它种高收入工作的所得还要多。<ref name="nowgamer"/>
  
《时空幻境》已被评论家推崇为大作，<ref name="npr">{{cite web | url = http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=94025221 | title = Xbox's 'Braid' A Surprise Hit, For Surprising Reasons | publisher = [[NPR|NPR]] | first = Heather | last = Chaplin | date = 2008-08-27 | accessdate = 2009-05-19 | archive-date = 2020-10-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201026110548/https://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=94025221 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/26336877 | title = Indie game designer earns raves for 'Braid' | publisher = [[MSNBC|MSNBC]] | date = 2008-08-22 | accessdate = 2009-05-27 | first = Winda | last = Benedetti | archive-date = 2012-10-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121026071054/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/26336877 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3172861 | title = Braid PC Listed for March Release on Impulse | first = Dustin | last = Quillen | date = 2009-02-18 | accessdate = 2009-05-27 | publisher = [[1UP.com|1UP.com]] | archive-date = 2009-02-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090226034303/http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3172861 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/editorials/reviews/5157-Review-Braid | title = Review: Braid | publisher = [[The_Escapist|The Escapist]] | date = 2008-08-21 | accessdate = 2009-05-27 | first = Earnest | last = Cavalli | archive-date = 2009-06-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090609150232/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/editorials/reviews/5157-Review-Braid | dead-url = no }}</ref>其显示的独特谜题受到高度赞扬。电子游戏网站[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]编辑丹·怀特海（Dan Whitehead）提到，在时间操控上的创新变化以及有必要去理解主角动作的非线性性质让他感到好似「长年蒙在眼上、只能看有限视野的游戏『马眼罩』被撕走了」。<ref name="eurogamer review"/>《[[世纪报_(澳大利亚)|澳大利亚世纪报]]》编辑杰森·希尔（Jason Hill）表示该游戏谜题是「精心制作且难以对付的」，不过「它被设计得无懈可击，解开它有着巨大的满足感。」<ref>{{cite news | first = Jason | last = Hill | date = 2008-08-21 | publisher = ''[[The_Age|The Age]]'' | title = Braid }}</ref>《先驱太阳报》周日版编辑帕迪·莱利（Paddy Reiley）重申了此一观点。<ref>{{cite news | publisher = ''[[Sunday_Herald_Sun|Sunday Herald Sun]]'' | first = Paddy | last = Reiley | date = 2008-08-17 | title = Braid New Worlds }}</ref>此外，谜题间的联系和游戏整体表现广受赞同被认为成标准；网站[[Gamespot|Gamespot]]编辑汤姆·麦克西亚（Tom McShea）表示《时空幻境》是个「罕见的游戏，让您这一刻绞尽脑汁解开谜题，下一刻又折服于其意味深长的故事。」<ref name="gamespot review"/>斯兰丹斯电影节暨游击游戏设计锦标赛游戏总监山姆·罗伯茨（Sam Roberts）对《时空幻境》留下了深刻的印象，「感觉不到一丝青涩」，因为它一如任何其他形式媒体般对玩家「期望很高」，且它「在任何方面都不把你看扁。」<ref name="npr"/>《时空幻境》美工与游戏呈现亦赢得了高度肯定。网站[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]的编辑尼克·苏特纳（Nick Suttner）评论说《时空幻境》的美工「将复古设计的纤巧与印象派背景及亲切的手绘环境并列」，<ref name="1up review"/>而[[Gamespot|Gamespot]]编辑麦克西亚指出，游戏的视觉效果「引人注目但从未让玩家分散注意力。」<ref name="gamespot review"/>《[[连线|连线]]》杂志编辑让·斯诺（Jean Snow）指出，《时空幻境》的「美丽的交响旋律让那些已经令人难忘而独特的观感锦上添花」，且「舒缓的音乐可能是当你面对刁钻谜题时却从未真正迷失的原因。」<ref name="wired review">{{cite web | url = http://blog.wired.com/games/2008/08/review-braid-in.html | title = Review: Braid Innovates and Satisfies | first = Jean | last = Snow | publisher = ''[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]]'' | date = 2008-08-13 | accessdate = 2009-02-20 | archive-date = 2009-03-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090303203243/http://blog.wired.com/games/2008/08/review-braid-in.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>游戏《[[杀手7|杀手7]]》与《[[英雄不再|英雄不再]]》的制作人[[须田刚一|须田刚一]]表示说玩《时空幻境》会让他想尝试搞个二维游戏。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.1up.com/do/newsStory?cId=3173747 | title = Goichi Suda, Fumito Ueda's Game Design Seminar | first = Kevin | last = Gifford | date = 2009-04-15 | accessdate = 2009-04-15 | publisher = [[1UP.com|1UP]]}}</ref>

《时空幻境》所遭致的批评主要是其游戏过短。[[IGN|IGN]]的编辑希拉里·戈尔茨坦（Hilary Goldstein）指出，一旦你已经完成了所有的谜题后，游戏让您「没有理由故地重游」。<ref name="ign review"/>但是，其他编辑们把《时空幻境》的游戏简短历程与有着类似批评的《[[时空枪|时空枪]]》相较，「在面对其独特的讲故事方式以及辽阔的思想时」，其游戏长度「可被忽视。」<ref name="1up review"/>游戏定价也被看作是本游戏的一项缺点，<ref>{{cite news | publisher = ''[[Toronto_Sun|Toronto Sun]]'' | title = Braid your head; Mario-like game will test your skills on the metaphysical level | first = Steve | last = Tilley | date = 2008-08-24 }}</ref>不过评语也指出，「《时空幻境》让您花的每块钱都值回票价。」<ref name="gamespot review"/>评论还指出，尽管布洛在整个游戏里试图整合故事与其他游戏元素，不过这只有在最后世界里达到效果，而除此之外本作故事是「在其不自然的晦涩下显得有点平庸。」<ref name="edge review"/>

本作PC版被视为「忠于」其Xbox 360版本，它保持同样的内容而没有增加任何新的功能。<ref name="ign pc review"/>编辑评论表示，《时空幻境》由于键盘作为控制装置而受益。<ref name="ign pc review"/>不过，作为Xbox 360版本的移植版本之一，PC版缺乏对用户电脑优化图形显示的初步支持， 如调整至较高屏幕分辨率或关闭某些游戏效果 ，编辑们认为这是该游戏的一大缺陷，但预计将公布补丁以添加这些选项。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.atomicgamer.com/article.php?id=770&page=1 |title=Braid PC Review |first=Jeff |last=Buckland |date=2009-04-14 |accessdate=2009-04-14 |publisher=[[AtomicGamer|AtomicGamer]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090415164704/http://atomicgamer.com/article.php?id=770 |archivedate=2009-04-15 }}</ref>

除了以其设计在2006年赢得独立游戏节奖之外，[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]选择了《时空幻境》作为其2008年「最佳原创下载家用机游戏」、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/best-of/special-achievement/index.html?page=9 |title=GameSpot's Best Games of 2008: Best Original Downloadable Console Game |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2008-12-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081223093239/http://www.gamespot.com/best-of/special-achievement/index.html?page=9 |archivedate=2008-12-23 }}</ref>「最佳跨平台游戏」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/best-of/genre-awards/index.html?page=5|title=GameSpot's Best Games of 2008: Best Platformer|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=2008-12-25|archive-date=2008-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081223092957/http://www.gamespot.com/best-of/genre-awards/index.html?page=5|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及「最佳授权音乐」等奖项得奖者，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/best-of/special-achievement/index.html?page=14 |title=GameSpot's Best Games of 2008: Best Licensed Music |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2008-12-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081223093052/http://www.gamespot.com/best-of/special-achievement/index.html?page=14 |archivedate=2008-12-23 }}</ref>而《官方Xbox杂志》则授予本作为2008年「Xbox Live Arcade年度游戏」、「最佳音乐」、「最佳结尾」得奖者，并名并列其「无可争辩、最不可思议年度游戏」得奖者之一。<ref>{{cite news | title = The 2008 Official Xbox Magazine Game of the Year Awards | publisher =  ''[[Official_Xbox_Magazine|Official Xbox Magazine]]'' #93 | date = February 2009}}</ref>《时空幻境》在第12届[[互动艺术与科学学院|互动艺术与科学学院]]颁奖典礼上被授予「年度休闲游戏奖」。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=22406 | title = LittleBigPlanet Dominates At AIAS Awards | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2009-02-20 | accessdate = 2009-02-20 | first = David | last = Jenkins | archive-date = 2009-02-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090221122858/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=22406 | dead-url = no }}</ref>《时空幻境》在2008年Xbox Live Arcade奖上总共受到5项提名<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=22508 | title = Braid, Capcom Lead 2008 XBLA Award Nominees | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2009-02-27 | accessdate = 2009-05-04 | first = Leigh | last = Alexander | archive-date = 2009-03-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090306102034/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=22508 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，且在「最佳创新」类赢得奖项。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=211469 | title = GDC: Castle Crashers tops Braid in XBLA Awards | publisher = [[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]] | date = 2009-03-24 | accessdate = 2009-05-04 | first = Andy | last = Robinson | archive-date = 2009-03-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090327121052/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=211469 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

